# Canvas debugging entry point

See the full architecture map and per-flow trace guides:

**[canvas/docs/DEBUGGING_GUIDE.md](canvas/docs/DEBUGGING_GUIDE.md)**

Quick enable (browser devtools, then reload):

```js
localStorage.setItem('canvas-sync-trace', '1');
localStorage.setItem('canvas-placement-audit', '1');
```

Legacy colon keys (`canvas:sync-trace`, `canvas:placement-audit`) also work.
